<subSubSection type="nomenclature">
<paragraph pageNumber="13">
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:135976" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Camponotus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Camponotus (Myrmotrema) troglodytes var. abyssinica Santschi" lsidName-HNS="Camponotus (Myrmotrema) troglodytes var. abyssinica Santschi" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="troglodites" subGenus="Myrmotrema" variety="abyssinica">Camponotus (Myrmotrema) troglodites Forel var. abyssinica</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel rank="variety">n. var.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="description">
<paragraph pageNumber="13">
— [[ queen ]]. Long. 10.5 mill. — Entierement jaune rougeatre (chez le type l'extremite du gastre est noire, il est entierement noir chez la var. Rhodesiana For.). La pubescence est interrompue en une bande mediane sur le gastre (comme chez le type, 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:26230" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Camponotus" genus.completionEvidence="missing" genus.completionRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Camponotus auropubens Forel" lsidName-HNS="Camponotus auropubens Forel" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="auropubens">auropubens</taxonomicName>
, etc.). Bien plus robuste que 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:26273" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Camponotus" genus.completionEvidence="missing" genus.completionRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Camponotus bottegoi Emery" lsidName-HNS="Camponotus bottegoi Emery" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bottegoi">bottegoi</taxonomicName>
Em.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="materials_examined">
<paragraph pageNumber="13">Abyssinie: Dire Doua (J. Roger).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="13">
. M. Forel vient de decrire une variete 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:180166" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Camponotus" genus.completionEvidence="missing" genus.completionRound="1" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Camponotus robecchii rhodesiana Forel" lsidName-HNS="Camponotus robecchii rhodesiana Forel" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodesiana">rhodesiana</taxonomicName>
, qu'il rattache a troglodites (dont le type est de Delagoa et non d'Abyssinie). D'apres la description, cette variete voisine beaucoup le G. Ilgii Forel.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
